00:37:59,001 --> 00:38:01,458
But I need to give these back to you.

613
00:38:02,842 --> 00:38:04,595
I don't get it.

614
00:38:04,595 --> 00:38:06,733
I can't meet you anymore.

615
00:38:06,733 --> 00:38:09,911
- Why? Did I do something wrong?
- No, no.

616
00:38:09,911 --> 00:38:14,344
- So why are you... 
- I need more time with Helen.

617
00:38:14,344 --> 00:38:16,077
But what about me?

618
00:38:16,077 --> 00:38:17,377
What do you mean?

619
00:38:17,377 --> 00:38:21,669
Dancing last night... that blew me away. 
I mean, it was hot.

620
00:38:21,669 --> 00:38:24,152
And now that you and my dad are done...

