00:38:28,230 --> 00:38:32,369
Jed, that's not...
I never meant to give you that idea.

624
00:38:33,182 --> 00:38:35,048
But I make you laugh.

625
00:38:35,048 --> 00:38:37,937
And on our driving lessons sometimes
you touch my hand.

626
00:38:37,937 --> 00:38:39,925
No, Jed, that's not what I meant.

627
00:38:39,925 --> 00:38:41,447
But you held me against you.

